01:54:25,566 --> 01:54:26,775
Gospodar je stigao.

894
01:54:28,900 --> 01:54:30,067
- Gospodaru.
- Gospodaru.

895
01:54:30,441 --> 01:54:31,274
Vratio se.

896
01:54:44,108 --> 01:54:48,358
Šta si videla.

897
01:54:49,441 --> 01:54:50,984
Ubice!

898
01:54:51,608 --> 01:54:55,066
Meišan je mrtva, ubice!

899
01:54:55,233 --> 01:54:59,692
Gluposti! Šta si videla?

900
01:55:00,483 --> 01:55:01,984
Ništa nisi videla!

901
01:55:02,525 --> 01:55:05,733
Ubice!

902
01:55:05,942 --> 01:55:11,108
Ti si luda! Poludela si!

903
01:55:11,984 --> 01:55:18,483
Ubice... vi ste ubice!

